snippet.title: Champion Strike 1:1 Mobile RTS game Trailer short v2
snippet.description:
Surprisingly simple champion movements lead to unexpected battle strategies.
Try to read the enemy champion’s movement and create your best counterplay!

Champion Strike, a direct interactive RTS mobile game, has soft-launched in the Philippines and Singapore.

Go to Google Play Store & Apple App Store - https://champ.onelink.me/lnBa/f39be090
